<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='832000' id='t-832000'>Now here's the deal.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='834000' id='t-834000'>These behaviors are just behaviors.</span>
